children-7 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-7 menuparent"><a href="/teaching-assistant-enrichment" class="sf-depth-1  menuparent">TA Enrichment</a><ul><li id="menu-2810-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/assistantships" class="sf-depth-2 ">Information about Assistantships</a></li><li id="menu-2811-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/campus-wide-new-ta-orientation" class="sf-depth-2 ">Campus-Wide New TA Orientation</a></li><li id="menu-2812-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/international-teaching-assistants-program-home-page" class="sf-depth-2 ">International Teaching Assistant Program (ITA)</a></li><li id="menu-2813-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/foundations-college-teaching-course-gc-593" class="sf-depth-2 ">Foundations of College Teaching Course - GC 593</a></li><li id="menu-2892-1" class="middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/practicum-college-teaching-course-gc-594" title="Practicum in College Teaching Course - GC 594" class="sf-depth-2 ">Practicum in College Teaching Course - GC 594</a></li><li id="menu-2893-1" class="middle even sf-item-6 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/teaching-uic-handbook-teaching-assistants" title="Teaching at UIC:  A Handbook for Teaching Assistants" class="sf-depth-2 ">Teaching at UIC:  A Handbook for Teaching Assistants</a></li><li id="menu-2894-1" class="last odd sf-item-7 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/center-advancement-teaching-learning-communities" title="Council for Excellence in Teaching and Learning" class="sf-depth-2 ">Center for the Advancement of Teaching-Learning Communities</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-2637-1" class="last even sf-item-8 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-3 sf-parent-children-1 sf-single-children-2 menuparent"><a href="/graduate-student-forms-publications" class="top-menu-parent sf-depth-1 menuparent">Forms &amp; Publications</a><ul><li id=